---
// AegisTalk 產品頁 — 規格 v1.2 §3.2（現站內容遷移+改寫；老陳故事線待 MAIC 語源到位後補）
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="AegisTalk 安心說 — 在加密通話內即時用 AI 攔截詐騙的家庭守護通訊 App"
  description="AegisTalk：端對端加密通訊 + 三層 AI 防詐（黑白名單/語意規則/行為基線）+ 免費家庭守護。僅透過官方應用商店發佈。"
  active="aegistalk"
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero" style="min-height:85vh">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="hero-badge"><img src="/img/aegistalk-logo.png" alt="" style="height:1.3em;vertical-align:-.3em;margin-right:.2em" />AegisTalk 安心說</div>
      <h1>全球第一支在加密通話內<br /><span class="gradient">即時用 AI 攔截詐騙</span>的通訊 App</h1>
      <p>
        訊息、通話、檔案全程端對端加密 —— 而 AI 守衛就站在對話現場：
        話術一出現，紅盾警示立刻彈出。分析全部在你的手機上完成，隱私毫髮無傷。
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="#download" class="btn-primary">取得 App</a>
        <a href="#protection" class="btn-ghost">三層防護怎麼運作 ↓</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 三層 AI 防護 -->
  <section class="ai-engine" id="protection">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">// AI PROTECTION</div>
      <h2 class="section-title reveal">三層防護，環環相扣</h2>
      <p class="section-desc reveal">由 AegisAI Core 驅動 —— 逾 26 萬行防詐引擎程式碼、53,640 條規則，全部跑在你的裝置上。</p>
      <div class="ai-layers">
        <div class="ai-layer reveal">
          <div class="layer-badge l1">L1</div>
          <div class="layer-info">
            <h4>黑白名單 · 毫秒級攔截</h4>
            <p>惡意網址、假冒域名（typosquatting）、詐騙關鍵詞 —— 已知威脅在 1 毫秒內攔下。</p>
            <div class="speed">&lt; 1ms</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ai-layer reveal">
          <div class="layer-badge l2">L2</div>
          <div class="layer-info">
            <h4>語意規則 × 機器學習融合</h4>
            <p>可解釋的專家規則 ⊕ fastText 語意模型（&lt;6MB）雙引擎融合 —— 抓得住規則沒見過的新話術。</p>
            <div class="speed">98.5% 偵測率 · F1 0.981（26,137 則實測，域內測試）</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ai-layer reveal">
          <div class="layer-badge l3">L3</div>
          <div class="layer-info">
            <h4>行為基線 · 異常偵測</h4>
            <p>26 維對話行為特徵 + Isolation Forest 在本地訓練你的互動基線 —— 「這個人突然變了」也逃不過。</p>
            <div class="speed">100% 本地訓練，資料不出裝置</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- AegisAI / AegisID 深度區（點按鈕看真實測試報告） -->
  <section class="moat">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">// UNDER THE HOOD</div>
      <h2 class="section-title reveal">三大內建模組 — 不只宣稱，附上實測</h2>
      <div class="eco-grid" style="margin-top:3rem;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(300px,1fr))">
        <div class="eco-card talk reveal">
          <div class="eco-step">AI 引擎</div>
          <h3>AegisAI</h3>
          <div class="tagline">三層防詐引擎</div>
          <p>
            L1 黑白名單毫秒攔截 → L2 53,640 條可解釋規則 × fastText（&lt;6MB）語意融合 →
            L3 26 維行為基線 Isolation Forest 本地訓練。逾 26 萬行引擎程式碼，
            98.5% 偵測率 / 99.6% 準確率 / F1 0.981（26,137 則實測，域內測試）。
          </p>
          <p style="margin-top:1.25rem">
            <a href="/aegistalk/aegisai-report/" target="_blank" class="btn-primary" style="display:inline-block;white-space:nowrap;padding:.6rem 1.2rem;font-size:.88rem"><svg width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="vertical-align:-.15em;margin-right:.25em"><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="10"></line><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="4"></line><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="16"></line></svg>AegisAI L2 實測報告 →</a>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="eco-card pay reveal">
          <div class="eco-step">身份引擎</div>
          <h3>AegisID</h3>
          <div class="tagline">裝置無關的生物身份</div>
          <p>
            AuraFace（ResNet100 + ArcFace）512 維臉部特徵向量 + YuNet 五點對齊 + 活體防偽。
            僅存向量、不存照片；換手機刷臉 + PIN 帳號原地回來。
            FEI 受控測試 FRR 0%、LFW 843 萬組比對驗證。
          </p>
          <p style="margin-top:1.25rem">
            <a href="/aegistalk/aegisid-report/" target="_blank" class="btn-primary" style="display:inline-block;white-space:nowrap;padding:.6rem 1.2rem;font-size:.88rem"><svg width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="vertical-align:-.15em;margin-right:.25em"><path d="M3 7V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2"></path><path d="M17 3h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v2"></path><path d="M21 17v2a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-2"></path><path d="M7 21H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-2"></path><path d="M9 9h.01"></path><path d="M15 9h.01"></path><path d="M9.5 14a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 5 0"></path></svg>AegisID 唯一性報告 →</a>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="eco-card vpn reveal">
          <div class="eco-step">支付風控模組</div>
          <h3>AegisPay</h3>
          <div class="tagline">付款前的最後一道閘門</div>
          <p>
            對話語境閘控 × 風險動態時間鎖（後悔期）× 簽章收款碼。安心幣（1:1 美元穩定幣）、
            ERC-4337 智能合約錢包、金鑰由 AegisID 身份衍生 —— 非託管，AegisRD 零金鑰。
            核心功能已完成鏈上實測（測試網）。
          </p>
          <p style="margin-top:1.25rem">
            <a href="/aegistalk/pay" class="btn-primary" style="display:inline-block;white-space:nowrap;padding:.6rem 1.2rem;font-size:.88rem"><svg width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="vertical-align:-.15em;margin-right:.25em"><path d="M21 12V7H5a2 2 0 0 1 0-4h14v4"></path><path d="M3 5v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16v-5"></path><path d="M18 12a2 2 0 0 0 0 4h4v-4Z"></path></svg>AegisPay 技術介紹 →</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 功能區塊 -->
  <section class="ecosystem">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">// FEATURES</div>
      <h2 class="section-title reveal">把守衛搬進對話現場</h2>
      <div class="eco-grid">
        <div class="eco-card talk reveal">
          <div class="eco-step">訊息防詐</div>
          <h3>紅盾警示</h3>
          <p>詐騙話術、惡意連結、可疑檔案 —— 訊息一到就在本地掃描，高風險即時彈出全螢幕紅盾，一鍵檢舉封鎖。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="eco-card vpn reveal">
          <div class="eco-step">通話防詐</div>
          <h3>語音即時分析</h3>
          <p>加密通話中，語音在你的裝置上即時轉文字並比對詐騙話術 —— 「猜猜我是誰」還沒講完，警示已經出現。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="eco-card pay reveal">
          <div class="eco-step">永久免費</div>
          <h3>Family Guard 家庭守護</h3>
          <p>爸媽的手機遇到高風險詐騙，你的手機立刻收到通知；定期報平安、惡意網址攔截 —— 全部免費。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="eco-card track reveal">
          <div class="eco-step">身份保證</div>
          <h3>AegisID 整合</h3>
          <p>臉部特徵向量 + PIN 的裝置無關身份 —— 換手機不掉帳號、好友不會被「假的你」冒充。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 實機截圖（沿用現站資產） -->
  <section class="screenshots">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">// SCREENSHOTS</div>
      <h2 class="section-title reveal">產品實機展示</h2>
      <div class="ss-scroll">
        <div class="ss-item"><img src="/images/talk-risk-alert.jpg" alt="紅盾風險警示" loading="lazy" /><div class="ss-label">詐騙話術即時紅盾</div></div>
        <div class="ss-item"><img src="/images/talk-ai-detect.jpg" alt="AI 偵測" loading="lazy" /><div class="ss-label">三層 AI 引擎偵測</div></div>
        <div class="ss-item"><img src="/images/talk-biometric.jpg" alt="AegisID 臉部辨識" loading="lazy" /><div class="ss-label">AegisID 臉部辨識</div></div>
        <div class="ss-item"><img src="/images/talk-add-friend.jpg" alt="安全加好友" loading="lazy" /><div class="ss-label">短碼／QR 安全加好友</div></div>
        <div class="ss-item"><img src="/images/guard-threat.jpg" alt="家庭守護警示" loading="lazy" /><div class="ss-label">Family Guard 威脅通知</div></div>
        <div class="ss-item"><img src="/images/guard-block.jpg" alt="惡意攔截" loading="lazy" /><div class="ss-label">惡意網址攔截</div></div>
        <div class="ss-item"><img src="/images/guard-database.jpg" alt="詐騙網址資料庫" loading="lazy" /><div class="ss-label">詐騙網址資料庫</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 下載區（規格 §3.2：商店徽章 + 反假冒聲明；不放 PWA 連結） -->
  <section class="cta-section" id="download">
    <h2>取得 AegisTalk</h2>
    <p>App Store 與 Google Play 上架準備中 —— 上架後此處將提供官方下載。</p>
    <div class="hero-actions" style="justify-content:center">
      <span class="btn-ghost" style="cursor:default"><svg width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="vertical-align:-.15em;margin-right:.25em"><path d="M12 20.94c1.5 0 2.75 1.06 4 1.06 3 0 6-8 6-12.22A4.91 4.91 0 0 0 17 5c-2.22 0-4 1.44-5 2-1-.56-2.78-2-5-2a4.9 4.9 0 0 0-5 4.78C2 14 5 22 8 22c1.25 0 2.5-1.06 4-1.06z"></path><path d="M10 2c1 .5 2 2 2 5"></path></svg>App Store · 準備中</span>
      <span class="btn-ghost" style="cursor:default"><svg width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="vertical-align:-.15em;margin-right:.25em"><path d="M12 8V4H8"></path><rect width="16" height="12" x="4" y="8" rx="2"></rect><path d="M2 14h2"></path><path d="M20 14h2"></path><path d="M15 13v2"></path><path d="M9 13v2"></path></svg>Google Play · 準備中</span>
    </div>
    <p style="margin-top:2rem;color:var(--warn);font-weight:700">
      <svg width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="vertical-align:-.15em;margin-right:.25em"><path d="m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3Z"></path><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"></line><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"></line></svg>AegisTalk 僅透過官方應用商店發佈 —— 任何「網頁版」皆為假冒詐騙。
    </p>
  </section>
</Base>
